    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> The build still fails but I can't reproduce the problem locally for the moment :(\n\nI dont know metalsmith-sass but it seems to force the node-sass dependency, instead of making it a peerDependency (allowing you to upgrade easily).\n\nMaybe you need to do `npm rebuild node-sass` on travis, but this might not be feasible given metalsmith-sass has it as a direct dependency.\n",
